# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Table 3: itertools.accumulate — bitwise operator dict-presence checks
#
# Wave 550 theme: accumulate is a C extension type (added in Python 3.2,
# extended with func parameter in 3.3). It supports arbitrary binary
# functions via its func parameter, but does not define bitwise operators
# directly in its own class __dict__; it is an iterator, not a numeric type.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

